{{Wiktionary|compressor|}} A '''[[compressor]]''' is a mechanical device that increases the pressure of a gas by reducing its volume.
'''Compressor''' may also refer to:
* A device that performs [[Compression (disambiguation)]] * [[Compressor (audio signal processor)]], for dynamic range compression * [[Compressor (software)]], a video and audio media compression and encoding application
